[p]From the Great Wall to the great temple cities of Indochina, from the foothills of Mount Fuji to the river valleys of China, an infinite array of new adventures and stories awaits you in [b][i]All Under Heaven[/i][/b], the largest expansion for [i]Crusader Kings III [/i]to date. The newly expanded map presents a rich and colorful setting for imperial ambition, sacred duties and shadowy scheming with detailed representations of medieval China, Japan and Southeast Asia.[/p][p][hr][/hr][/p][p][dynamiclink href="https://youtu.be/YxJo9ZSg6Ik"][/dynamiclink][/p][p]Coming on 28 October, [b][i]All Under Heaven[/i][/b] takes your campaigns to entirely new settings, unseen in any previous [i]Crusader Kings [/i]game. Keep a steady hand on the regional hegemon or manage the tumult of dynastic change in China. Revere the Yamato emperor and his regent in Japan, or pursue the path of the samurai warlord. Build a monumental temple facility in the jungles of Southeast Asia and compel weaker kingdoms to pay tribute to your greatness.[/p][p]
[b][i]All Under Heaven [/i][/b]also introduces Japanese as a supported language for [i]Crusader Kings III[/i], further expanding the international audience that has grown to support this royal game.[/p][p][/p][p][dynamiclink href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3315530/Crusader_Kings_III_All_Under_Heaven/"][/dynamiclink][/p][h1]Features of All Under Heaven[/h1][list][*][p][b]China: The Mandate of Heaven[/b][/p][list][*][p]Ascend to the highest tier of power with the new [i]Hegemony[/i] title, reigning supreme over all empires in the Chinese region.[/p][/*][*][p]Navigate the [i]Dynastic Cycle[/i], a living system of stability and chaos. Exploit periods of instability to rise to power and reshape the political landscape.[/p][/*][*][p]Explore the [i]Celestial [/i]government system, unique to China. Earn [i]Merit[/i] through deeds or the [i]Imperial Examinations[/i], gaining favor and influence.[/p][/*][*][p]Manage the [i]Imperial Treasury[/i] to fund [i]Great Projects[/i], defend against disasters, or expand your influence with statecraft and might.[/p][/*][/list][/*][*][p][b]Japan: Rise of the Shogunate[/b][/p][list][*][p]Take control of a Japanese house and forge your destiny. Rise through the intricate courtly system to become a mighty Shogun or Kampaku regent.[/p][/*][*][p]Strengthen your position through alliances, intrigue, and ritual, or unite the houses through the strength of your samurai armies; which path you take is for you to decide.[/p][/*][*][p]Lead the Imperial Yamato house to restore power to the Emperor, ushering in an age of imperial grandeur.[/p][/*][*][p]Experience the rich cultural traditions of Japan, where honor and scandal intertwine, shaping the lives of lords and vassals alike.[/p][/*][/list][/*][*][p][b]Southeast Asia: God-Kings and Temple Empires[/b][/p][list][*][p]Rule as a [i]Devaraja[/i] with the Mandala Government, uniting tributaries into vast, temple-centered empires.[/p][/*][*][p]Pay tribute to the God King by performing [i]Tributary Missions[/i] as a Tributary ruler, increasing favor with your subjects.[/p][/*][/list][/*][*][p][b]Explore the Silk Road, new Starting Bookmarks and Historical Flavor[/b][/p][list][*][p]Thrive along the expansive [i]Silk Road[/i] by profiting from the wealth and innovations of China, even if you are far beyond its borders.[/p][/*][*][p]New historical starting bookmarks bring fresh perspectives and new challenges. Play as iconic characters from the past or forge your unique path.[/p][/*][*][p]Immerse yourself in  Asia's cultural, artistic, and historical nuances with new throne rooms, events, and traditions.[/p][/*][/list][/*][*][p][b]And much more[/b][/p][/*][/list][p][/p][p]Whether you aim to unify Japan under your family clan, claim the Mandate of Heaven in China, or thrive as a God-King in Southeast Asia, [b][i]All Under Heaven[/i][/b] expands the boundaries of [i]Crusader Kings III[/i] on a monumental scale.[/p][p][/p][p][b][i]All Under Heaven [/i][/b]will be available on [b]28 October 2025[/b], and is also available as part of the Chapter IV bundle.
[/p][hr][/hr][p][/p][p]Chapter IV of [i]Crusader Kings III[/i] invites you to explore the struggles of the nomadic way of life and the splendor of Eastern Asia. With a rich lineup of content releasing throughout 2025, Chapter IV brings new challenges, systems, and customization options that deepen your gameplay and expand the game map in thrilling new ways.[/p][p][/p][p][dynamiclink href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3486700/Crusader_Kings_III_Chapter_IV/"][/dynamiclink][/p]